            <h2 style="text-align: center;">
             <strong>
              Welcome to the Office of Human Resources.
             </strong>
            </h2>
            <p>
             In concert with the mission of the university, we value and encourage excellence, integrity, creativity, and critical thinking. We strive to foster an inclusive environment that will promote employee success and attract a diverse array of high performing professionals.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
             <a class="cta-button" href="/about-hr">
              ABOUT HR
             </a>
            </p>
            <div class="views-field views-field-body envelope-page-body">
             <div class="field-content">
              <div class="envelope contextual-links-region envelope-narrow envelope-style-green">
               <div class="grid-1col">
                <div class="grid-item">
                 <h2 style="text-align: center;">
                  Human Resources Units
                 </h2>
                 <p style="text-align: center;">
                  The Office of Human Resources serves and supports departments and units across campus in delivering effective human resources management.
                 </p>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
